工具介绍：
一款简约的XPATH表达式解析器。
在左侧文本框中输入要解析的 XPATH 表达式，并且支持XPath内正则表达式，如/div[*]/div[1]。

Tool Introduction:
A minimalist XPATH expression parser.
Enter the XPATH expression to be parsed in the text box on the left, and it supports regular expressions within XPath, such as /div[*]/div[1].
